# Superstore-Sales-analysis (Excel dashboard)

## project overview
This project analysis Superstore Sales data using Excel. The objective is to clean the dataset, analyze sales performance, and create an interactive dashboard using pivot tables and charts.
The dashboard provides insights into sales performance across different regions, product categories, and customer segments.

## Tools used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot tables
- Data cleaning

## Dataset used
- I used the Superstore sales dataset (Rohit Sahoo) for this project.

## Dashboard Features
- Sales by Region
- Sales by Category
- Sales by customer Segment
- Year-wise sales trend

## Dashboard Insights
- West region generates high sales.
- Technology category contributed the largest revenue.
- Sales increased steadily across the observed years.
- consumer segment has the more sales.

